==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Waney
<hw>Wan"ey</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A sharp or uneven edge
on a board that is cut from a log not perfectly squared, or that is made
in the process of squaring. See <er>Wany</er>, <pos>a.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wang</ent>⟦br⟧
